# RCPassThru Mode - Bypass ArduSub Internal Mixer
# Maps RC Channel inputs directly to Servo Outputs (no internal mixing)
# RC1 → Output1, RC2 → Output2, etc.
# This allows our custom mixer to have full control over motor PWMs.

SERVO1_FUNCTION 51
SERVO2_FUNCTION 52
SERVO3_FUNCTION 53
SERVO4_FUNCTION 54
SERVO5_FUNCTION 55
SERVO6_FUNCTION 56
SERVO7_FUNCTION 57
SERVO8_FUNCTION 58
